{"tid":1301563,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【大家點睇】要保持號召力，焦點應轉向追究黑警","createTime":"2019-07-09T16:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T15:05:35.000Z","uid":164729,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4bead2929ddca434d1dfe4230d95d77a02b54635","tid":1301563,"uid":164729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:23:57.000Z","msg":"依家好多人聽到林鄭條7婆話條例壽終正寢<br />\n好多中立派已經收貨<br />\n但一講起警察暴力 好多無立場市民都會認同<br />\n尤其經過6/7包護娜娜、送打人個廢老上的士<br />\n7/7旺角對路人無理動武後<br />\n警察已經周圍辣慶火頭 連藍絲都燒著埋<br />\n依家係再結集民意既好機會<br />\n<br />\n希望大家緊記香港人善忘呢一點<br />\n襯社會各界仲嬲係到仆街<br />\n開展新戰線 追究黑警<br />\n咁同時要求政府釋放義士同爭取雙普選等訴求都可以同時推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地要鞏固民意呀！！<br />\n記住，政府唔怕民意，都唔怕抗爭，<br />\n但政府最怕有民意既抗爭！</span><br />\n<br />\n求大家同意既幫我推上去<br />\n希望大家認清目標"},{"pid":"f6fa3d0ac8eee44b11b36b7eda5457e5ceaca39f","tid":1301563,"uid":164729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:24:26.000Z","msg":"<code>我無野講</code>"},{"pid":"fa3414eebf7c1668e9dfcd228e7d0aebbed0ece8","tid":1301563,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AiR3F8V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAiR3F8V.jpg&h=f4a2740b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuDmAd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuDmAd2.jpg&h=28455d55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9108a29c6648d0d1a326fcb317fa19dcd8e24aff","tid":1301563,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:24:55.000Z","msg":"屌你老母2019年仲有人覺得做警察有好人"},{"pid":"25a59d50e1f222bf04a83c00d3fa87cba80657d7","tid":1301563,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:25:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>7.10</strong> - <ins>麥小姐追思會</ins> ＠ 中環愛丁堡廣場 - 19:00~22:30<br />\n<strong>7.11</strong> - <ins>梁烈士公眾告別禮</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/leun